text: Rennes School of Business is an European higher studies establishment. The school is in Rennes, France. It has been established in 1990.L'ESC Rennes accréditée Equis Rennes SB is specialist in the fields of economics, social sciences and management. ==References== == Further reading == * Rennes SB website Category:1990s establishments in France Category:1990 establishments in Europe Category:Education in France Category:Rennes
